&quot;Not true,&quot; I inform him. &quot;You should see the margins of my student papers.&quot;
&quot;Not the same as writing a book though, right?&quot;
&quot;Almost identical,&quot; I assure him. &quot;Both go largely unread." -- Richard Russo
